# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for InstCombine:

[InstCombine][profcheck] Add unknown branch weights to selects created in InstCombineAndOrXor.cpp
These select instructions were created from combinations of bitwise operators which have no branch weight information.

Tracking issue: #147390
